  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\n`CachedBeaconState` is duplicating the entire `BeaconState`. This is a huge waste of memory.\r\n\r\nInstead, it should take a reference to `BeaconState`\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nI think this would be best done with an `Arc`, using lifetime specifiers (e.g., `'a`) will be a bit burdensome.\r\n",
